From 5c3019fca1d85533f34735bf40c97156c87b6d4f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ilya Gulya <ilya@gulya.me>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 15:46:12 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] xnu: establish E-UNION core filesystem semantics

Consolidate path resolution, copy-up, whiteout and opaque-directory handling, merged directory enumeration, activation, and foundational path detranslation into one reviewable block.

The colocated behavioral fixtures and resolver test remain part of this block.
---
 .../libsystem_kernel/emulation/CMakeLists.txt |  12 +
 .../linux_premigration/vchroot_expand.h       |  21 +
 .../linux_premigration/vchroot_userspace.c    | 936 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../bsd/impl/dirent/getdirentries.c           |  13 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/fcntl/openat.c   |  14 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/network/bind.c   |  31 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/stat/mkdirat.c   |   9 +-
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/stat/mkfifo.c    |   7 +-
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/stat/rmdir.c     |   7 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/time/utimes.c    |  11 +-
 .../bsd/impl/unistd/chmod_extended.c          |   9 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/close.c   |  12 +
 .../xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/fchmodat.c    |  10 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/linkat.c  |  14 +
 .../src/xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/mknod.c   |   6 +-
 .../xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/renameat.c    |  23 +
 .../xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/symlinkat.c   |   8 +-
 .../xnu_syscall/bsd/impl/unistd/truncate.c    |  11 +-
